    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Depthdrops is a 3D puzzle game inspired by the classic BlockOut game for DOS.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move and rotate the pieces along the 3 axes (except backwards) and aim for the highest score.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>2 game modes:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <i>Classic</i>: Play the game with the classic puzzle pieces.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <i>Relaxing</i>: Same as Classic mode but you will not level up, the fall speed will not change.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Gamepad Support</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports PS4/PS5 and Xbox controllers. with more to come.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Widescreen Support</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16:9 and 32:9 Aspect ratios supported in both Windowed and Full-Screen</p>",
